# Netflix Titles Search Flask App

A simple Flask web application to search and filter Netflix titles by **title** and **type** (genre-like filtering replaced by type).  
Displays results in a clean, Netflix-inspired dark-themed UI with pagination and summary statistics.

---

## Features

- Search Netflix titles by **title** and **type** (e.g., Movie, TV Show)
- Paginated results with next/previous navigation
- Summary statistics showing counts of titles by rating
- Clean and responsive UI styled with CSS (no JavaScript or Bootstrap)
- Dark mode-inspired Netflix vibes with black background and signature red highlights
- Clear filters button to reset search inputs
- "No results found" message when no titles match the search


